$interpreted: Ru-yi: Sophie~what does it say in the letter?
Sophie: Let's see...
Sophie: A clue——the color of a fire lizard's scales...
Sophie: Red! Why didn't she just tell us!?
Clark: It's a thief's job to hide from the light of truth. All professions have a negative side, but a thief...*sigh*...what a waste of talent.
Maria: Detecting new vocabulary..."profession"...analyzing.
Maria: Master! Wonderful news! The chances of you experiencing the negative effects of a profession are zero. The reason is that you don't have a job.
Clark: *cough*...thank you, Maria.
Hutchinson: Everybody, look. There's a ruby over there...
Ru-yi: Wah! It's so beautiful~
Sophie: Looks just like this one!
Sophie: ...A real secret passage!
Ru-yi: It's pitch black in there. I can't even see the end of the passage. So scary! Are we going in? What if we don't come back?
Rune: Don't be afraid. I will...protect us.
Hanbei: I hope it's that easy.
Sophie: ...Let's go.
Hutchinson: Waaahh! ...I nearly fell over...it's hard to walk when you can't see the ground.
Clark: Everybody, stop.
Ru-yi: Eh? Huh? Do I hear something?
Maria: Clark, it's so shiny~
Clark: A Rune Lens...I did extensive research on these at the Academy. Luckily, I keep this on me at all times. Let's put it to use~
Sophie: Water...this is an underground waterway...
Hanbei: Ugh! My shoes are all wet. Disgusting.
Clark: Located underneath the Oasis Casino?
Clark: It must the old waterway that connects to the oasis' water reserves. Looks pretty badly damaged. Must have been abandoned a long time ago.
Rune: Sophie, do you want to keep going?
Sophie: Yeah. Elio may be in here. We can't give up.
Ru-yi: It's sooo dark. I'm scared...I kind of want to go back~~
Sophie: Ru-yi, please don't cry. It's already too wet here.
Ru-yi: But-But...
Sophie: Ru-yi, quit tugging on me. It's dangerous!
Ru-yi: But-But-But I'm sc-sc-scared...who knows what's hiding in the water...
Sophie: What are you scared of? You weren't afraid of beating up those guards. There's no monster down here that's scary than hu——
Rune: Noise.
Ru-yi: Som-Som-Som-Something's down here!!!!
Sophie: Calm down. It's probably just a mouse. It's normal for mice to live down here...
Sophie: ...Right, Clark?
Clark: It's hard to say. I wouldn't be surprised if there were traps set up down here.
Hanbei: What!? So we're in danger?
Rune: I'll walk ahead. If there's danger...I'll find it.
Sophie: Rune!?
Rune: Elio is Sophie's friend. Elio is Rune's friend too.
Clark: ...Okay, then. Rune, let's walk ahead. Everyone else be careful. Maria, make sure they don't run into anything abnormal.
Maria: Received! Detection system activated!
Hutchinson: Excuse me, am I mistaken? Or do I feel something sticky on my feet?
Clark: Everybody, stop for a second.
Hutchinson: What is this? Why is there a spider's nest here?
Hanbei: Looks like there's a lot of them...
Hanbei: Hey! It's too dangerous to keep going. Best turn around...
Maria: Biological organisms detected! Biological organisms detected!
Ru-yi: It's a spider! It's definitely a spider coming to eat us! What are we going to do!!?!?
Hanbei: Let's get out of here!
Sophie: Wait a sec! Look!
Sophie: Someone's trapped over there. That's what that noise was...!
Hanbei: We've got no time for that, Sophie. If we keep going, we'll be in trouble too!
Hanbei: Did you forget how Morgan died?
Sophie: I...
Rune: Rune...will go.
Hanbei: You butthead. Did you not hear what I said?
Rune: Must...help.
Hanbei: How!? The spider web is way too high! How are you going to do that?
Clark: If we aim at the edge of the web, we should be able to pull it down.
Hanbei: ...Whatever, let's just get this over with!!
Sophie: Oh no!! It's coming down!!
Hanbei: You dummies!!!!!
Sophie: Rune? What...is that? That person...she...
Rune: That...is not a person.
Hutchinson: Is this...really a spider...? Didn't that look like a person's head?
Hanbei: Of course it's a spider. Look, it has eight legs.
Rune: Sophie...what is this?
Clark: Maria, can you identify this organism?
Maria: Order received. Maria is processing!
Maria: Oh...it self-dissolved. Scan failed.
Sophie: Dissolved!?
Hutchinson: What a bizarre sight...what on earth is it?
Ru-yi: Disgusting~~~
Sophie: Ah, yes! Don't you remember? Sanchez said that the High Priest was capturing people for an experiment...
Sophie: There's no way that this is...
Sophie: ——What!? This trap is designed to look like a human.
Hanbei: Yeah, and it's meant to catch idiots like you.
Sophie: But it also means we're on the right path.
Ru-yi: But-But...
Hanbei: Ain't no "buts" about it! Let's get going!
Sophie: ......
Sophie: No...way...
